00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:09.999
and how it has already transformed scholarship.

00:31:10.000 --> 00:31:12.999
I have a wonderful in-house storage. In December 2009,

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:15.999
the President issued an executive order announcing the

00:31:16.000 --> 00:31:19.999
declassification center at the national archives which

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:23.999
